'''腰骶神經叢'''是由{{le|腰神經|lumbar nerve}}、{{le|薦神經|sacral nerve}}，以及{{le|尾神經|coccygeal nerve}}组成。有時候胸下神經的分支也會參與神經叢的形成。

腰骶神經叢可分為下列部分：
* {{le|腰神經叢|lumbar plexus}}
* {{le|薦神經叢|sacral plexus}}
* {{le|陰部神經叢|pudendal plexus (nerves)}}

腰骶神經叢的損傷大多源自於骨骼損傷，常見症狀為{{Le|腰薦神經|Lumbosacral trunk}}和{{le|薦神經叢|sacral plexus}}麻痺<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Garozzo|first1=Debora|last2=Zollino|first2=Gianluca|last3=Ferraresi|first3=Stefano|title=In lumbosacral plexus injuries can we identify indicators that predict spontaneous recovery or the need for surgical treatment? Results from a clinical study on 72 patients|journal=Journal of Brachial Plexus and Peripheral Nerve Injury|date=January 11, 2014|volume=9|issue=1|doi=10.1186/1749-7221-9-1|url=http://www.jbppni.com/content/9/1/1}}{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

